1
00:00:25,480 --> 00:00:27,080
ADAPTED FROM THE WEBCOMIC YI REN ZHI XIA

2
00:00:31,479 --> 00:00:32,680
THIS IS A WORK OF FICTION

3
00:00:32,759 --> 00:00:35,120
ALL ACTIONS AND ABILITIES PERFORMED SHOULD NOT BE IMITATED

4
00:00:36,680 --> 00:00:37,720
Die, all of you!

5
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:58,599
Ms. Bao.

6
00:01:01,760 --> 00:01:03,320
Why didn't you dodge it?

7
00:01:04,800 --> 00:01:06,360
You told me to stand here.

8
00:01:15,840 --> 00:01:17,240
See?

9
00:01:17,320 --> 00:01:18,520
I didn't move.

10
00:01:36,240 --> 00:01:38,160
The bleeding isn't stopping.

11
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:48,679
Ms. Bao, I am so sorry.

12
00:01:50,199 --> 00:01:51,399
Ms. Bao!

13
00:01:51,479 --> 00:01:52,800
Wake up!

14
00:01:52,880 --> 00:01:54,559
Open your eyes, Ms. Bao!

15
00:01:57,839 --> 00:01:58,679
I…

16
00:01:58,759 --> 00:01:59,960
I won't run away again.

17
00:02:01,399 --> 00:02:02,440
I'll…

18
00:02:02,520 --> 00:02:04,720
I'll be your obedient servant from now on.

19
00:02:14,239 --> 00:02:16,640
That wiped your smirk away.

20
00:02:16,720 --> 00:02:18,359
Now you've witnessed the might

21
00:02:18,440 --> 00:02:20,079
of my Dragon-Piercing Awl.

22
00:02:26,079 --> 00:02:27,920
I must have lost my mind

23
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:30,680
expecting anything from a scoundrel who ambushes a girl

24
00:02:30,760 --> 00:02:32,519
who has lost the will to fight!

25
00:02:42,880 --> 00:02:43,920
Chulan,

26
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:44,880
let me see.

27
00:02:46,880 --> 00:02:48,079
Xingtong, come here.

28
00:02:49,239 --> 00:02:50,600
Dad, let me handle it.

29
00:02:59,440 --> 00:03:00,840
What are you doing?

30
00:03:01,480 --> 00:03:02,600
Chulan, don't worry.

31
00:03:02,679 --> 00:03:05,400
This is Dispatch of Detained Spirits, our family heirloom.

32
00:03:05,480 --> 00:03:06,880
The primordial spirit that we detain

33
00:03:06,959 --> 00:03:08,840
will grant us some of the power they had

34
00:03:08,920 --> 00:03:10,239
when they were alive.

35
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:19,160
The spirit I summoned

36
00:03:19,239 --> 00:03:20,640
is the healer

37
00:03:20,720 --> 00:03:22,280
known as one of the Nine Great Savants,

38
00:03:22,359 --> 00:03:23,640
Mr. Wang Zizhong.

39
00:03:23,720 --> 00:03:24,600
When he was alive,

40
00:03:24,679 --> 00:03:26,160
he was a miraculous healer.

41
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:34,040
Her liver has been pierced.

42
00:03:34,119 --> 00:03:35,399
Her qi can't be balanced.

43
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:38,320
Chairman Feng.

44
00:03:39,959 --> 00:03:41,959
Had I stepped in in time,

45
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:43,959
none of this would've happened.

46
00:03:46,679 --> 00:03:48,000
Move aside.

47
00:03:48,760 --> 00:03:49,720
Have you lost your mind?

48
00:03:49,799 --> 00:03:50,760
She could die!

49
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:52,200
Don't worry.

50
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:54,160
Her life is our responsibility.

51
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:56,720
Zhang Chulan,

52
00:03:56,799 --> 00:03:58,560
is this how you protected Baobao?

53
00:04:02,640 --> 00:04:04,079
Xu San, give me a hand.

54
00:04:07,239 --> 00:04:09,119
When did Baobao become so heavy?

55
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:17,200
By the way, Chairman Feng,

56
00:04:17,279 --> 00:04:19,519
regarding the incident that took place here today,

57
00:04:19,599 --> 00:04:22,159
NDT Express will punish those responsible.

58
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:23,800
We will pay for the damage

59
00:04:23,880 --> 00:04:25,479
inflicted on your staff and property.

60
00:04:29,320 --> 00:04:30,560
Chairman Feng, so…

61
00:04:30,640 --> 00:04:31,479
Don't worry.

62
00:04:32,080 --> 00:04:34,800
I will give NDT Express an explanation.

63
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,880
Can you please drive faster?

64
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:54,120
The guy from the Feng family provided first aid.

65
00:04:54,200 --> 00:04:55,039
Calm down a little.

66
00:04:57,120 --> 00:04:58,919
A PLACE TO EAT

67
00:05:00,320 --> 00:05:01,240
I like that restaurant.

68
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:02,599
We can get some food there later.

69
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:04,960
This is not the way to the hospital.

70
00:05:05,039 --> 00:05:06,880
Their salt-fried meat with potatoes

71
00:05:06,960 --> 00:05:08,280
pairs well with rice.

72
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:11,159
And the sautéed guts smell amazing.

73
00:05:13,479 --> 00:05:14,640
Have you lost your mind?

74
00:05:14,719 --> 00:05:15,960
Head to the hospital!

75
00:05:16,719 --> 00:05:18,000
We should first send them back.

76
00:05:25,840 --> 00:05:26,800
Chulan?

77
00:05:26,880 --> 00:05:28,280
I told you to wait inside the room.

78
00:05:28,359 --> 00:05:29,520
Why did you come out?

79
00:05:32,159 --> 00:05:33,440
This is your last meal.

80
00:05:33,520 --> 00:05:34,479
Have something decent.

81
00:05:34,960 --> 00:05:36,599
Xu San and I

82
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:38,400
bought your favorite food for you.

83
00:05:38,479 --> 00:05:39,880
While you're still breathing,

84
00:05:39,960 --> 00:05:41,440
enjoy the tasty smell of it.

85
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,599
If you have anything to tell her,

86
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:46,800
you should do so now.

87
00:05:48,640 --> 00:05:49,599
Ms. Bao.

88
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:54,000
I don't know if you can hear me,

89
00:05:54,080 --> 00:05:55,599
but I have to tell you.

90
00:05:56,919 --> 00:05:58,479
You apologized to me,

91
00:05:59,359 --> 00:06:00,800
but I still owe you an apology.

92
00:06:02,080 --> 00:06:03,880
Over the years, aside from my grandfather,

93
00:06:04,719 --> 00:06:06,719
no one has treated me like you did.

94
00:06:08,919 --> 00:06:10,359
You risked your life to keep me safe.

95
00:06:11,840 --> 00:06:13,320
Ms. Bao,

96
00:06:13,400 --> 00:06:14,520
you gave me

97
00:06:14,599 --> 00:06:16,560
the warmth of a family that I never had.

98
00:06:18,840 --> 00:06:21,039
I stubbornly argued with you not long ago.

99
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:24,159
I regret it now.

100
00:06:26,840 --> 00:06:27,719
Chulan.

101
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:30,359
What is your plan

102
00:06:30,440 --> 00:06:31,880
for after her passing?

103
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:33,520
Ms. Bao wants me to go to Mount Longhu.

104
00:06:34,159 --> 00:06:35,440
So that is where I will go.

105
00:06:35,520 --> 00:06:37,880
She wants me to join the Outsider Martial Arts Contest.

106
00:06:39,159 --> 00:06:40,840
I will do what she wants

107
00:06:42,760 --> 00:06:43,799
and win Tianshidu.

108
00:06:58,799 --> 00:07:00,880
So stop whining and start training.

109
00:07:01,520 --> 00:07:03,520
Ms. Bao. What's going on?

110
00:07:03,599 --> 00:07:04,680
I took a nap. I woke up because I was hungry.

111
00:07:04,760 --> 00:07:06,479
Xu Si said you were dying!

112
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:19,400
What is going on?

113
00:07:19,479 --> 00:07:20,520
We're not very sure either.

114
00:07:20,599 --> 00:07:22,479
But Baobao has a powerful self-healing ability.

115
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:24,159
I stopped the Feng boy from healing her

116
00:07:24,239 --> 00:07:25,640
so her secret wouldn't be exposed.

117
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,680
You lied to me in the car!

118
00:07:28,799 --> 00:07:30,159
You don't get so sad very often.

119
00:07:30,239 --> 00:07:31,599
We couldn't bear to interrupt you.

120
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:33,359
I had to pinch my leg to hold my laughter.

121
00:07:33,440 --> 00:07:35,799
Zhang Chulan, I recorded everything.

122
00:07:36,440 --> 00:07:37,680
Go to Mount Longhu

123
00:07:37,760 --> 00:07:38,960
and be the champion.

124
00:07:39,039 --> 00:07:41,239
Win Tianshidu.

125
00:07:42,919 --> 00:07:43,960
Tie this to your legs.

126
00:07:44,039 --> 00:07:45,239
We'll continue our training today.

127
00:07:45,320 --> 00:07:46,719
We're patrolling the mountainside.

128
00:07:46,799 --> 00:07:47,919
If you ever complain,

129
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:49,479
I'll teach you a lesson.

130
00:07:52,520 --> 00:07:54,400
Did you buy all these for me?

131
00:07:54,479 --> 00:07:55,680
Yes, these are all yours.

132
00:07:57,280 --> 00:07:58,200
Ms. Bao.

133
00:07:58,280 --> 00:07:59,840
Simmered snow fungus.

134
00:07:59,919 --> 00:08:01,440
This should bolster your qi.

135
00:08:10,719 --> 00:08:12,280
Ms. Bao, I…

136
00:08:12,359 --> 00:08:13,440
I can't…

137
00:08:14,320 --> 00:08:15,520
I can't run anymore, Ms. Bao!

138
00:08:15,599 --> 00:08:16,560
What did you say?

139
00:08:16,640 --> 00:08:17,880
Is it too slow?

140
00:08:17,960 --> 00:08:18,799
Okay!

141
00:08:20,520 --> 00:08:23,919
19 DAYS UNTIL THE OUTSIDER MARTIAL ARTS CONTEST

142
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,800
13 DAYS TO GO

143
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:30,240
12 DAYS TO GO

144
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:37,760
10 DAYS TO GO

145
00:10:00,560 --> 00:10:03,920
7 DAYS UNTIL THE OUTSIDER MARTIAL ARTS CONTEST

146
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:11,600
Lamp,

147
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:13,280
turn on the lights.

148
00:10:28,680 --> 00:10:29,680
Master Lu.

149
00:10:30,680 --> 00:10:31,560
Master Fang.

150
00:10:32,640 --> 00:10:34,120
Master Hong asked me

151
00:10:34,199 --> 00:10:35,640
to relay a message to you.

152
00:10:36,839 --> 00:10:38,120
He went ahead of you.

153
00:10:38,959 --> 00:10:40,640
You need not be sad about his passing.

154
00:11:19,439 --> 00:11:21,160
I know the whole truth now.

155
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:22,800
What should I do?

156
00:11:33,400 --> 00:11:34,400
Don't touch it!

157
00:11:40,959 --> 00:11:42,400
Remember to stop the man I was.

158
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:45,000
Do not let him find out the truth.

159
00:12:02,199 --> 00:12:04,400
It seems I have no choice

160
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:07,040
but to visit Mount Longhu myself.

161
00:12:08,319 --> 00:12:11,880
MOUNT LONGHU

162
00:12:13,520 --> 00:12:15,680
Lingyu, are you awake?

163
00:12:19,480 --> 00:12:20,560
What is it?

164
00:12:20,640 --> 00:12:21,800
Grandmaster asked for you.

165
00:12:23,160 --> 00:12:24,160
Just yesterday,

166
00:12:24,240 --> 00:12:26,400
Mr. Lu and Grandmaster were on the phone.

167
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:29,079
He took a flight to Mount Longhu to show his support overnight.

168
00:12:29,160 --> 00:12:31,439
He supposedly brought a special guest with him.

169
00:12:31,520 --> 00:12:32,640
-A guest? -Yes.

170
00:12:32,719 --> 00:12:34,360
The guest came specially for you.

171
00:12:35,040 --> 00:12:36,560
For me?

172
00:12:58,880 --> 00:12:59,800
Mr. Lu.

173
00:12:59,880 --> 00:13:01,199
LU JIN

174
00:13:01,280 --> 00:13:02,560
Lingyu.

175
00:13:03,880 --> 00:13:05,520
-Come out! -Stop it.

176
00:13:05,599 --> 00:13:06,959
You kept saying you wanted

177
00:13:07,040 --> 00:13:08,599
to meet Spirit Master Lingyu.

178
00:13:08,680 --> 00:13:09,880
Now that we are here,

179
00:13:09,959 --> 00:13:10,800
why are you hiding?

180
00:13:10,880 --> 00:13:12,640
Lingyu, I must apologize

181
00:13:12,719 --> 00:13:14,199
for spoiling my granddaughter rotten.

182
00:13:14,280 --> 00:13:15,800
Don't mind her.

183
00:13:19,680 --> 00:13:20,560
Lingyu,

184
00:13:21,079 --> 00:13:23,280
I was told you've been training meticulously

185
00:13:23,360 --> 00:13:25,839
in preparation for the Outsider Martial Arts Contest.

186
00:13:25,920 --> 00:13:27,560
I am not interested in Tianshidu.

187
00:13:27,640 --> 00:13:29,480
I just don't want to bring shame to my master.

188
00:13:32,160 --> 00:13:33,040
Linglong,

189
00:13:33,520 --> 00:13:35,079
this is your first time here.

190
00:13:35,160 --> 00:13:36,560
When I was a young man,

191
00:13:36,640 --> 00:13:38,240
I was a regular guest on this mountain.

192
00:13:38,319 --> 00:13:40,760
It has been ages since I last came here.

193
00:13:41,680 --> 00:13:42,560
I've grown old myself.

194
00:13:42,640 --> 00:13:44,480
I'm afraid I'm running out of time to be here.

195
00:13:44,560 --> 00:13:46,959
You're not old. You're only a little over a century old.

196
00:13:47,040 --> 00:13:48,160
Mr. Lu,

197
00:13:48,240 --> 00:13:50,760
the contest is three days from now.

198
00:13:50,839 --> 00:13:51,880
You summoned the elders

199
00:13:51,959 --> 00:13:53,800
when the contest is just around the corner.

200
00:13:54,400 --> 00:13:55,839
Privately, they have

201
00:13:55,920 --> 00:13:57,319
some doubts and objections.

202
00:13:57,880 --> 00:13:59,079
Fear not.

203
00:13:59,160 --> 00:14:00,560
I have my own reason

204
00:14:00,640 --> 00:14:01,800
for bringing them here.

205
00:14:02,520 --> 00:14:05,160
Your master and I are so close.

206
00:14:06,040 --> 00:14:08,400
He wants to announce the Outsider Martial Arts Contest

207
00:14:08,480 --> 00:14:10,199
to the entire Outsiders' world.

208
00:14:10,280 --> 00:14:11,439
I have to help him

209
00:14:11,520 --> 00:14:13,240
accomplish this great undertaking.

210
00:14:14,920 --> 00:14:15,959
Yes.

211
00:14:22,240 --> 00:14:23,160
Yes.

212
00:14:23,240 --> 00:14:25,599
I'm going to see your master.

213
00:14:25,680 --> 00:14:26,680
Linglong.

214
00:14:27,280 --> 00:14:29,360
Show Linglong around the place.

215
00:14:29,439 --> 00:14:30,599
Have a look around.

216
00:14:30,680 --> 00:14:32,079
Don't go, Grandpa!

217
00:14:35,280 --> 00:14:36,760
Spirit Master Lingyu.

218
00:14:37,400 --> 00:14:39,120
Our country has some truly picturesque views.

219
00:14:39,199 --> 00:14:40,880
Let's have a look around the mountain.

220
00:14:41,439 --> 00:14:43,120
Sure. Make yourself at home.

221
00:14:48,520 --> 00:14:49,839
I caught a cold.

222
00:14:49,920 --> 00:14:50,880
Are you all right?

223
00:14:50,959 --> 00:14:52,280
We do have an infirmary here.

224
00:14:53,280 --> 00:14:54,920
I'll feel better after some walking.

225
00:14:55,839 --> 00:14:56,839
Actually,

226
00:14:56,920 --> 00:14:59,800
I've had a fever since this morning. My temperature is 39 degrees Celsius.

227
00:14:59,880 --> 00:15:01,120
Is it 39 degrees Celsius?

228
00:15:02,760 --> 00:15:03,959
I'm lightheaded.

229
00:15:04,040 --> 00:15:05,240
Impressive.

230
00:15:07,920 --> 00:15:08,839
Chief Celestial Taoist,

231
00:15:08,920 --> 00:15:11,560
you announced that the heir selection will be an open contest.

232
00:15:11,640 --> 00:15:14,199
Only the Ten Elders can intervene.

233
00:15:14,280 --> 00:15:15,319
In that case,

234
00:15:15,400 --> 00:15:17,479
they can go after your title

235
00:15:17,560 --> 00:15:19,479
and get their hands on Qi Apotheosis.

236
00:15:20,199 --> 00:15:22,280
This allows the stranger Zhang Chulan

237
00:15:23,160 --> 00:15:25,160
to participate in the Outsider Martial Arts Contest

238
00:15:25,240 --> 00:15:28,079
and compete for a place to inherit the title.

239
00:15:28,160 --> 00:15:30,719
I can understand why they reacted this way.

240
00:15:30,800 --> 00:15:32,560
All these people

241
00:15:32,640 --> 00:15:34,079
covet Qi Apotheosis.

242
00:15:34,160 --> 00:15:35,959
But I don't get it.

243
00:15:36,040 --> 00:15:38,280
If you take Zhang Chulan in,

244
00:15:38,360 --> 00:15:40,160
those old geezers may hate it,

245
00:15:40,240 --> 00:15:41,599
but they won't object.

246
00:15:41,680 --> 00:15:43,280
Why do you insist on putting him

247
00:15:43,360 --> 00:15:44,959
in the contest?

248
00:15:45,040 --> 00:15:46,280
The Jiashen Calamity

249
00:15:46,959 --> 00:15:48,520
left too many enduring complications.

250
00:15:49,719 --> 00:15:51,360
Zhang Chulan is the key to it all.

251
00:15:52,400 --> 00:15:53,479
But without some training,

252
00:15:53,560 --> 00:15:55,240
the duty is too heavy for him.

253
00:15:55,880 --> 00:15:57,160
The Jiashen Calamity?

254
00:15:58,240 --> 00:15:59,880
So is this what worries you?

255
00:16:00,520 --> 00:16:02,120
I'll give you a hand.

256
00:16:02,199 --> 00:16:04,079
From the hottest fire comes the strongest steel.

257
00:16:14,160 --> 00:16:15,240
Take a seat.

258
00:16:15,880 --> 00:16:17,079
I didn't summon you.

259
00:16:17,680 --> 00:16:19,280
It was Lu Jin who gathered you here.

260
00:16:20,640 --> 00:16:21,640
Take a seat.

261
00:16:24,479 --> 00:16:26,400
Master Jiekong, Guan Shihua, and Na Ruhu

262
00:16:26,479 --> 00:16:27,359
couldn't make it.

263
00:16:27,439 --> 00:16:29,479
They wanted me to apologize on their behalf.

264
00:16:29,560 --> 00:16:30,400
Very well.

265
00:16:33,040 --> 00:16:34,439
THE TEN ELDERS

266
00:16:34,520 --> 00:16:38,240
A GROUP CONSISTING OF THE MOST RESPECTED OUTSIDERS.

267
00:16:38,319 --> 00:16:42,560
WHENEVER THERE ARE CONFLICTS BETWEEN FACTIONS OF OUTSIDERS,

268
00:16:42,640 --> 00:16:45,319
THEY SHALL FACILITATE AND NEGOTIATE TO MAINTAIN PEACE.

269
00:16:45,400 --> 00:16:46,719
Lu Jin,

270
00:16:47,479 --> 00:16:49,079
I thought we had settled the details

271
00:16:49,160 --> 00:16:50,680
for the Outsider Martial Arts Contest.

272
00:16:50,760 --> 00:16:53,920
What else could warrant a meeting?

273
00:16:55,359 --> 00:16:57,479
The Outsiders' world has this long-standing rule.

274
00:16:58,800 --> 00:17:01,400
For the sake of this contest,

275
00:17:01,479 --> 00:17:02,800
each of you

276
00:17:02,880 --> 00:17:04,720
has sent your most capable apprentice.

277
00:17:04,800 --> 00:17:07,200
I appreciate your effort and thoughts.

278
00:17:11,680 --> 00:17:13,079
But what about me?

