579
00:33:10,600 --> 00:33:11,600
You will become

580
00:33:11,679 --> 00:33:13,080
even stronger.

581
00:33:13,159 --> 00:33:15,879
If you present yourself as Hu Sheng,

582
00:33:15,959 --> 00:33:17,480
no one will suspect you.

583
00:33:23,080 --> 00:33:24,360
All right.

584
00:33:24,439 --> 00:33:25,800
The four of us don't get

585
00:33:25,879 --> 00:33:27,199
to gather around very often.

586
00:33:27,280 --> 00:33:28,639
Xia He, get over it.

587
00:33:28,719 --> 00:33:30,159
Let us all wish you

588
00:33:30,240 --> 00:33:31,520
a happy birthday.

589
00:33:33,280 --> 00:33:36,120
