591
00:33:38,919 --> 00:33:42,040
Happy birthday to Xia He

592
00:33:44,639 --> 00:33:46,600
For me, my birthday

593
00:33:46,679 --> 00:33:48,679
is reliving a dream of the past.

594
00:33:52,320 --> 00:33:53,919
Many years ago, on your birthday,

595
00:33:54,959 --> 00:33:56,560
on the street you liked,

596
00:33:57,159 --> 00:33:58,360
the two of us met.

597
00:33:58,959 --> 00:33:59,879
Xia He,

598
00:34:00,760 --> 00:34:01,879
today is your birthday.

